<h1>Appointment Cancelled</h1>

<p>Hi {{customerName}},</p>

<p>
    This is to confirm that your appointment has been cancelled.
</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3>Cancelled Appointment Details</h3>
    <p><strong>Title:</strong> {{appointmentTitle}}</p>
    <p><strong>Original Date & Time:</strong> {{formatDate startTime "long"}} at {{formatDate startTime "time"}}</p>
</div>

{{#if cancellationReason}}
<div class="info-box" style="background-color: #fef3c7; border-left-color: #f59e0b;">
    <h3>Cancellation Reason</h3>
    <p>{{cancellationReason}}</p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<h2>What's Next?</h2>
<p>
    If you'd like to reschedule or book a new appointment, please contact us:
    <br><br>
    Phone: <strong>{{organizationPhone}}</strong>
    <br>
    Email: <strong>{{organizationEmail}}</strong>
</p>

<p>
    We understand that schedules change. We're here whenever you're ready to move forward with your project.
</p>

<div class="info-box" style="background-color: #dbeafe; border-left-color: #3b82f6;">
    <h3>Questions?</h3>
    <p>
        If you have any questions about this cancellation or need assistance with anything else,
        please don't hesitate to reach out to us.
    </p>
</div>

<p>
    Best regards,<br>
    <strong>The {{organizationName}} Team</strong>
</p>